
'''瘟疫与人'''（{{lang-en|''Plagues and Peoples''}}）是历史学家[[威廉·H·麦克尼尔|威廉·H·麦克尼尔]]创作的一本关于[[流行病学|流行病]]的[[历史|历史]]书籍，1976年由 Anchor Books（[[Vintage_Books|Vintage Books]]的前身）出版。书中介绍了[[天花|天花]]在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]，[[腺鼠疫|腺鼠疫]]在中国以及[[斑疹傷寒|斑疹傷寒]]在欧洲的影响。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Whelchel |first1=Aaron |title=Book Review |url=http://worldhistoryconnected.press.illinois.edu/3.1/br_whelchel.html |website=World History Connected |date=2005-10 |access-date=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2018-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180128150314/http://worldhistoryconnected.press.illinois.edu/3.1/br_whelchel.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=PLAGUES AND PEOPLES {{!}} Kirkus Reviews |url=https://www.kirkusreviews.com/book-reviews/william-h-mcneill/plagues-and-peoples/ |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Retro Review: William H. McNeill - Plagues and Peoples (1976) |url=https://cei.org/blog/retro-review-william-h-mcneill-plagues-and-peoples-1976/ |website=Competitive Enterprise Institute |language=en-us |access-date=2021-03-01 |archive-date=2020-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918105648/https://cei.org/blog/retro-review-william-h-mcneill-plagues-and-peoples-1976 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

